comments.text: jstests is currently disabled on all platforms, but tinderbox shows it works fully on linux, even though there are problems on other platforms. So we should turn it on on linux at least, to try and prevent further regressions.
comments.raw_text: jstests is currently disabled on all platforms, but tinderbox shows it works fully on linux, even though there are problems on other platforms. So we should turn it on on linux at least, to try and prevent further regressions.
This patch turns on jstests on linux only. That's the only platform on which they all work for all combinations of JITFLAGS.
